----------------------------------------------------------------------
HONEST-CLAIM tags
----------------------------------------------------------------------

This project enforces an honest-marketing CI grep
(`scripts/honest_marketing_check.py`) that bans phrases such as
"world first", "SOTA", "perfect", "guaranteed", "完全自動", "永続" from
the README, RESULTS.md, and source docstrings. Performance numbers in
RESULTS.md must carry a `[MEASURED YYYY-MM-DD]` tag and a corresponding
bootstrap 95% CI. Implementation novelty is qualified with
"to our knowledge" and demoted on counter-evidence (see S0_GATE.md).
